                <img src="/img/headshot.jpg" alt="Judy Nguyen" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full object-cover mx-auto mb-6 shadow-md" />
                <div class="text-lg space-y-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    <p>
                        I'm a Computer Programming and Analysis student at Seneca Polytechnic in Toronto, Ontario,
                        expecting to graduate in 2028. I like building things across the stack, from small web apps
                        like this one to my first Unity game.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Outside of coursework, I've started dabbling in hackathons and creative coding, and I spend
                        a fair bit of time making digital art and sprites. This site is a running project as I learn
                        more about full-stack development.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

