                                <h3 class="card-title">MusicFromDaHeart</h3>
                                <p>Built at Hack the 6ix 2026. Turns real-time heart rate and Apple Pencil input into generative instrumental music that crossfades between calm, energetic, and tense moods.</p>
                                <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                                    <a href="https://devpost.com/software/musicfromdeheart" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline">Devpost</a>
