                                <h3 class="card-title">Utopia</h3>
                                <p>Built at HuskyHack 2026. A Ren'Py visual novel following a legal immigrant's encounter with ICE, where a real-time suspicion meter decides whether you make it through the night.</p>
                                <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                                    <a href="https://devpost.com/software/utopia-itj3qh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline">Devpost</a>
